quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,155,"(Ndetse twarabavumye) kubera kwica isezerano kwabo rikomeye, guhakana amagambo ya Allah, kwica abahanuzi babarenganyije ndetse no kuvuga bati \"Imitima yacu irapfundikiye (ntiyumva)\". Ahubwo Allah yarayidanangiye kubera ubuhakanyi bwabo, bityo ntibemera uretse gake"
  4,156,Kandi (twarabavumye) kubera ubuhakanyi bwabo n’imvugo yabo yuje ikinyoma gihambaye bagiriye Mariyamu (bamushinja ubusambanyi)
  4,157,"No k’ubw’imvugo yabo igira iti \"Rwose twishe Mesiya Isa (Yesu) mwene Mariyamu (Mariya), Intumwa ya Allah\". Nyamara ntibamwishe ntibanamubambye; ahubwo (bishe kandi banabamba) uwahawe ishusho ye. Kandi mu by’ukuri, babandi batabivuzeho rumwe, baracyamushidi- kanyaho (bibaza niba uwishwe yari Yesu cyangwa usa nawe). Nta bumenyi nyakuri babifiteho usibye gukurikira ibyo bakeka. Kandi rwose ntibamwishe"
  4,158,"Ahubwo Allah yamuzamuye iwe. Kandi Allah ni Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Ushishoza"
  4,159,Kandi nta n’umwe mu bahawe igitabo utazamwemera mbere yo gupfa kwe 41. Kandi no ku munsi w’imperuka azaba umuhamya wabo
  4,160,"Kubera ibikorwa bibi by’Abayahudi no gukumira (abantu) cyane kugana inzira ya Allah, twabaziririje ibyiza (mu biribwa) byari bibaziruriwe"
  4,161,"No kwakira Riba42 kwabo kandi barayibujijwe, ndetse no kurya imitungo y’abantu kwabo mu buriganya. Kandi abahakanyi muri bo twabateguriye ibihano bibabaza"
  4,162,"Cyakora, abacengeye mu bumenyi muri bo n’abemera; bemera ibyo wahishuriwe ndetse n’ibyahishuwe mbere yawe; (bakemera) abahozaho amasengesho, abatanga amaturo, ndetse n’abemera Allah n’umunsi w’imperuka; abo tuzabahemba ibihembo bihambaye"